  "title": "IT Project Manager (CAPM/PMP/SCRUM/CCNA)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Support ongoing technical projects and ensure clients receive timely and effective assistance.</li>\n  <li>Plan, track, and manage project activities, schedules, and resources to ensure on-time delivery.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with internal teams and external partners to meet project goals and resolve issues quickly.</li>\n  <li>Monitor project costs, prepare status reports, and ensure quality standards and customer requirements are met.</li>\n  <li>Maintain detailed project documentation and communicate updates to management regularly.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in IT or Cybersecurity, with certifications like <strong>CAPM, PMP, Scrum, CCNA, or ITIL v3</strong>.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience in <strong>IT project management </strong>with a customer-focused and proactive approach.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication skills with the ability to explain IT technologies and processes clearly.</li>\n  <li>Ability to manage small to mid-sized IT projects, ensuring deadlines are met and tasks are completed effectively.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701<br>\nRegistration: R21100996</p>",
